36:46.120 --> 36:47.712
It's a...

36:47.880 --> 36:50.314
- It saves your soul.
- Hmm?

36:50.520 --> 36:53.159
The thing I give you... what?

36:54.080 --> 36:59.791
The little piece of bread that
you just gave me, it saves your soul.

37:00.680 --> 37:02.955
- What? What?
- Are you worried about me?

37:03.120 --> 37:05.509
- What?
- It saves your soul.

37:05.680 --> 37:08.194
- Do you know what soul means?
- No.

37:08.360 --> 37:11.193
- It's like strength.
- Hmm.

37:13.120 --> 37:17.238
Why does the old man
keep his teeth in a glass at night?

37:19.240 --> 37:22.232
It's where he keeps his strength.

37:22.400 --> 37:24.152
His spirit.

37:24.320 --> 37:27.949
His spirit is in those teeth.

37:31.240 --> 37:32.832
Yeah.

37:33.000 --> 37:35.116
Oh, you're missing a little strength.

37:36.760 --> 37:39.718
- Right in the front of your mouth.
- Mm-mmm.

37:42.160 --> 37:44.549
The chapel's in the main block,
isn't it?

37:44.720 --> 37:47.393
Yes. What happened
with the black bandit?

37:49.520 --> 37:50.999
I'm sorry.

37:53.200 --> 37:54.599
It's ok.

37:57.840 --> 38:00.877
They keep the medicine
in the main block, don't they?

38:01.040 --> 38:02.314
Yes.

38:22.120 --> 38:26.671
That which has been taken from me
can never be replaced.

38:28.000 --> 38:29.274
My brother.

38:29.440 --> 38:32.830
- Why he speaks like this?
- He's your father.

38:33.000 --> 38:34.991
But my father's dead.

38:35.680 --> 38:37.318
What?

38:38.600 --> 38:41.512
