want him to speak?

38:41.680 --> 38:44.433
I think of all the joys we had.

38:44.640 --> 38:46.631
Normal, like you.

38:46.800 --> 38:49.155
I could have saved you,
but I was weak.

38:51.240 --> 38:54.789
My grief has gone
blood-red with revenge.

38:56.640 --> 38:58.995
I'm stronger now.

39:00.920 --> 39:05.550
I will search the four corners
of this earth, find governor odious

39:05.720 --> 39:07.358
and joyously kill him.

39:10.400 --> 39:15.872
By the blue bandit's honour I swear,
I will annihilate him...

39:16.040 --> 39:18.349
And everything that he loves.

39:24.200 --> 39:27.670
I will destroy him!

39:27.840 --> 39:32.231
I will destroy him!
I will destroy him!

39:32.400 --> 39:35.551
I will destroy him! Destroy him!

39:37.360 --> 39:40.113
And every Spanish thing.

39:41.400 --> 39:44.233
I thought he was Spanish?

39:44.400 --> 39:48.075
No... he was French.

39:48.240 --> 39:50.674
Are you with me, bandits?

39:51.560 --> 39:53.630
Oui, mon capitaine.

