47:05.440 --> 47:08.238
Because it makes you look...

47:10.120 --> 47:11.792
Pretty...

47:15.360 --> 47:17.715
And healthy, too.

47:21.280 --> 47:23.794
- Back before lunch.
- I know!

47:23.960 --> 47:26.076
Alexandria, no licking the ice today?

47:26.240 --> 47:29.038
No. Thank you. Bye!

47:40.840 --> 47:44.071
One bite maybe.
But a pit of snakes?

48:31.080 --> 48:37.519
M-0o-r-p-h-i-n-three.

48:41.960 --> 48:45.919
M-0o-r-p-h-i-n-three.

48:54.080 --> 48:57.038
R-p-h-i-n-three.

49:10.040 --> 49:14.192
Maybe you got...

49:14.360 --> 49:18.672
It's important you listen to me.
Think of your other children.

49:18.840 --> 49:20.796
I'm so sorry.

49:20.960 --> 49:24.714
Warn your children about rattlesnakes.

49:24.880 --> 49:30.159
This isn't a good time. There are
snake pits all over this area.

49:36.400 --> 49:39.995
Wake up! Wake up! You better get up
