when something frightens me?

50:29.800 --> 50:31.358
I say the magic words.

50:33.920 --> 50:38.198
Googly, googly, googly, begone.

50:41.920 --> 50:44.434
Let's practise together.

50:44.640 --> 50:46.198
The magic words.

50:47.400 --> 50:50.437
Googly, googly, googly. Go away.

50:57.600 --> 51:01.149
- Did you get what I sent you for?
- Yes.

51:02.680 --> 51:04.591
- This it is.
- Yeah?

51:06.920 --> 51:10.037
- There's only three.
- You asked me for three.

51:10.200 --> 51:13.272
